DESCRIPTION:Got a question about contributing to the Microsoft 365 & Power 
	Platform community? This is the place to bring it.\n\nOffice Hours is an o
	pen\, informal drop-in session held every other Tuesday at 9:30 AM PT...a 
	half hour after the weekly community call.\nNo agenda\, no prerequisites\,
	 and no wrong questions.\nWhether you're figuring out your first contribut
	ion\, working through something specific\, or just want to see what others
	 are building\, you're welcome here.\nDrop in when it works for you and po
	p out when you're done. The full session runs one hour.\nWhat to bring: An
	y question on your mind...GitHub\, Pull Requests\, community calls\, blog 
	posts\, documentation\, presenting\, badges\, or anything else related to 
	contributing.\nJoin the session: https://pnp.ms/sic-officehours-join <http
	s://pnp.ms/sic-officehours-join> \n<https://pnp.ms/sic-officehours-join> M
	ore info: https://pnp.ms/sharingiscaring <https://pnp.ms/sharingiscaring> 
	\n
